<a href="/questions/1008315-would-this-be-appropriate-for-8th-grade">Would this be appropriate for 8th grade students?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1008315'><a id="like_count_community_question_1008315" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1008315?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F35220.The_Red_Badge_of_Courage">like</a></span>

